data.description: Discover this captivating and rare newer constructed modern gem, offering the perfect blend of form and function. Inside, the well-designed floor plan showcases three spacious bedrooms and two updated bathrooms. Stylish finishes throughout the home from the leathered granite countertops to the wood like tile floors. Elevated for added peace of mind, surrounded by durable Hardie Board siding and impact resistance glass, and boasting a new sleek standing seam metal roof, . This residence sits on an oversized lot with potential for a pool, and just a short stroll away from Sanibel's pristine beaches making this property an island lover's dream.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this stylish, hurricane-resilient island retreat.
